What you need to know:

KBF assistant secretary general Ambrose Kisoi Thursday told Nation Sport that Kenya plans to host qualifiers for two groups between February 19 to 21Kisoi noted that because of Covid-19 pandemic, the government has to commit itself to ensure that health protocols will be implemented for Kenya's bid to be successfulKisoi confirmed that Cliff Owuor will still be in charge of Morans despite being appointed head coach of Rwandan side APR until 2022/23 season